description:
In this edition of The 21st of SepTrender, Jack and Miles discuss JJ Redick retiring, Ben Simmons being done with the 76ers, Joy Reid's 'missing white woman syndrome' theory, the Trump campaign knowing voting machine claims were false, 'the Many Saints of Newark' reviews, and a relationship tip from Bennifer LoFleck
